# Memory Tree Feature

- Implement memory tree as a generic domain model.
- Keep cache adapters replaceable (in-memory first, file/db later).
- Track `lastAccessedUtc` for pruning decisions.
- Prune deterministically with stable ordering.
- Keep session payload compact and backend-context focused.
- Never mutate node payloads after creation; create new nodes instead.
